A morning to glow from within.✨
We’re bringing together some of your favorite voices for The Yoga Glow Up, a mindful flow that’s all about slowing down, stretching out, and reconnecting with the self. 🌞🧘‍♀️

🗓 21st June, 2025

📍Evolve Studio, New Delhi

Follow along as our girlies tap into the power of stillness and movement and maybe even inspires your own glow up.

(The Yoga Glow Up, Kica Creators, Wellness with Kica, Yoga Glow Up event, Mind Body Soul wellness, International Yoga Day 2025, influencer yoga event, flow and glow session, glow from within experience)

✨ Classes designed to move with you. Whether you love the energy of a group or need a focused 1-on-1 session, there’s space for you at EVLVE. 

Element-based group classes + personalised training that actually works.
Strength, mobility, mindfulness — all under one calm, powerful space.

DM to join a class or book your PT session now.

#EvlveWithUs #DelhiFitnessStudio #SainikFarms #YogaAndStrength #MobilityTraining

I’m Shreya Sethi—Founder of EVLVE Studio, Counselling Psychologist,  Yoga & Movement Educator with over 11 years of experience.

I teach yoga, Pilates, strength training and mobility—in both group classes and personal training sessions—while also guiding yoga psychotherapy for emotional well-being.

EVLVE is my vision for a space where you can evolve—physically, mentally, and emotionally.
